                "name": "Puffball",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "A fungus leshy can spit a puffball as a standard action. If it hits, this attack deals 1 point of damage (this damage is not modified by Strength) and affects the target struck (but not adjacent targets) with the fungus leshy\u2019s spores. The puffball has a range increment of 20 feet."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "name": "Spores",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "A fungus leshy is riddled with molds and spores. Anytime a fungus leshy takes damage, a cloud of spores bursts from its body, forcing all adjacent creatures to make a DC 14 Fortitude save or have their vision reduced to 10 feet for 1 minute. Spending a full-round action to wash one\u2019s eyes with water ends this effect. The save DC is Constitution-based."
